OL,3,CFerry worker jailed for 20 months
OL,4,Cfollowing fatal boat collision
OL,6,FA Condor Ferry worker who endangered
OL,7,Flives after his vessel collided with a
OL,8,Ffishing trawler has been handed a 20-
OL,9,Fmonth prison sentence.
OL,11,FLewis Peter Carr, from Sunderland,
OL,12,Fappeared at Jersey's Royal Court on
OL,13,FThursday 4 December to receive his
OL,14,Fsentence.
OL,16,FHe was found guilty in a trial this
OL,17,FSeptember of endangering ships,
OL,18,Fstructures, or individuals - contrary
OL,19,Fto Jersey's Shipping Law.
