OL,6,FThe collision resulted in the deaths
OL,7,Fof Skipper Michael Michieli, Jervis
OL,8,FBaligat, and Larry Simyunn, who were
OL,9,Faboard the L'Ecume II.
OL,11,FClaire Michieli, Michael's wife, told
OL,12,Fthe court before sentencing that the
OL,13,Ftrial was "exhausting both emotionally
OL,14,Fand mentally."
OL,16,FIn her victim impact statement, she
OL,17,Fsaid the collision could have been
OL,18,Favoided if the defendants had
OL,19,Fperformed their duties properly.
