OL,6,F"My hope was this would provide
OL,7,Fanswers," she stated. "This will never
OL,8,Fundo the hurt and distress caused."
OL,10,FA letter from the family of Larry was
OL,11,Falso read out: "Larry was a loving,
OL,12,Fkind and good provider. It was Larry's
OL,13,Fdream to work in Jersey and work hard
OL,14,Fto get a good salary and provide for
OL,15,Fhis family.
OL,17,F"We lost our brother. Larry is gone.
OL,18,FThis fact is so painful to accept -
OL,19,Fthere is nothing you can do to bring
OL,20,Fhim back."
