OL,6,FThey were both accused of three counts
OL,7,Fof manslaughter and the fourth lesser
OL,8,Fcount of endangerment - the pair
OL,9,Fdenied all the charges.
OL,11,FMr Sevash-Zade was found not guilty of
OL,12,Fthe manslaughter charges and formally
OL,13,Fdischarged of the fourth, lesser
OL,14,Fcharge as the jury could not reach a
OL,15,Fverdict.
OL,17,FCarr was discharged of manslaughter
OL,18,Fcharges after the jury failed to reach
OL,19,Fa verdict.
