OL,6,FStates of Jersey Police have released
OL,7,Fa statement paying tribute to the
OL,8,Fvictims of the L'Ecume II collision.
OL,10,F"Our thoughts remain with the families
OL,11,Fof Michael Michieli, Jervis Baligat,
OL,12,Fand Larry Simyunn following today's
OL,13,Fsentencing," the statement reads.
OL,15,F"This marks the conclusion of one of
OL,16,Fthe most complex investigations we've
OL,17,Fundertaken.
